<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>
    Welcome <%-name%>
  </title>

  <%- include('../styles-global.ejs') %>
    <%- include('./styles-welcome-admin.ejs') %>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="root-wrapper mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-sm">Hello,<span class="mr-1 blue-1">
        <%-name%>
      </span>
    </h1>
    <div class="blue-2 text-lg font-bold">We are happy to have you onboard!</div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <p>You now have admin access, which allows you to do a lot of things into our system.</p>

      <p>Use this access key to login: <span class="font-bold">
          <%-access_key%>
        </span></p>

      <p>
        For better security, we generate an <span class="font-semibold">access key</span> for you to be able to login
        for the first time and,
        it should be
        noted that it is <span class="font-semibold">mandatory to choose a strong password on the first login!</span>
      </p>

      <div class="mx-auto my-10 w-max block">
        <p class="mb-2 font-semibold">Click the button below for your first login:</p>

        <div class="mx-auto w-max">
          <a target="_blank" href="http://accounts.fikani.com/login?access_key=CgVdl2">
            <button class="btn mt-2 white-1 bg-blue-1 rounded-lg py-3 px-6 uppercase text-lg font-bold">
              Login
            </button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 my-6 text-sm">
        <p>In case you need further assistance, write to us on</p>
        <a class="text-[#387ebf]" href="mailto:support@fikani.com">support@fikani.com</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm">Thank you, <span class="font-semibold">FIKANI Digital</span>.</div>


    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>